LC refers to the communication layer itself

LCM refers to the message type specification 

---------------

lcmgen   - Parses lcm type specifications, generating language-specific
           implementations

lcm-logger   - Minimalist logging implementation.

liblcm       - C runtime implementation of LCM

lcm-java     - Java runtime implementation of LCM, plus logging tools

lcm-python   - Python runtime implementation of LCM
